m\": 1517, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"a busy year\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But you have to grow up, you have no choice.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no choice\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was a junior, stepping into a professional environment and it was so strict.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a professional environment\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to work hard.\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watching Usain at training was just incredible.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Usain\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was looking up to him, studying him on YouTube every day.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999999999899956, \"rank\": 1.0140036473590193e-11, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was motivation.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"motivation\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw him dying on the track.\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he's working hard and already the world's fastest man, what do I have to do?\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just tried to compete.\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember he said to my coach: 'Who's this little boy?'\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"this little boy\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came home and shouted: 'Mummy, I ran with Usain in training!'\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Usain\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a very good relationship, he will give me a fist pump and he congratulated me after Budapest.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999296483135, \"rank\": 7.035183337876919e-08, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very good relationship\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"a fist pump\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I still look up to him.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to respect the man, he changed the sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hughes has gathered immense momentum after a breakthrough last year, banishing his Tokyo Olympics demons after squandering an opportunity in the 100m due to a false start.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2345, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.999999987830961, \"rank\": 7.904753992924234e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"immense momentum\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"a breakthrough\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2402}, {\"ngram\": \"his Tokyo Olympics demons\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"a false start\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a series of blazing runs last summer, he is now the British record holder over the 100m (9.83 seconds) and 200m (19.73 seconds).\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"blazing runs\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2547}, {\"ngram\": \"the British record holder\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"9.83 seconds\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"19.73 seconds\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, lightning struck twice to snatch two 30-year-old records from \\u200b\\u200bBritish icons Linford Christie and John Regis.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2738, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Linford Christie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\"}, {\"begin\": 2759, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Regis_(athlete)\", \"score\": 0.9999872251534899, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Regis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Regis_(athl